name: Kylo Ren
description:
Is a fictional character and a major antagonist in the Star Wars franchise, introduced in the 2015 film The Force Awakens.
Trained by his uncle Luke Skywalker as a Jedi, Ren was seduced to the dark side of the Force by Supreme Leader Snoke, and aspires to be as powerful as his grandfather, the Sith Lord Darth Vader.
Is also the master of the Knights of Ren, as well as a high-ranking member and later the Supreme Leader of the First Order.

#006 Star Wars Pack
